description:

The 'Kill switch' can be used to block apps from connecting to the internet if the Tor network cannot be reached.
To activate the 'Kill switch':

* Launch the Tor VPN app and tap on 'Configure'.
* Tap on 'Kill switch'.
* Tap on Tor VPN settings (⚙️).
* Toggle on 'Always-on VPN'.